Title: Determinant representations of scalar products for the open XXZ chain  with non-diagonal boundary terms
Authors: Wen-Li Yang and Xi Chen and Jun Feng and Kun Hao and Bo-Yu Hou and Kang-Jie Shi and Yao-Zhong Zhang
Abstract: With the help of the F-basis provided by the Drinfeld twist or factorizing F-matrix for the open XXZ spin chain with non-diagonal boundary terms, we obtain the determinant representations of the scalar products of Bethe states of the model.
